“User sends HTTPS request → Apache web server on EC2 handles it → PHP executes WordPress → WordPress interacts with MySQL database → response is sent back to user.”


Golden Rules (remember this)
user_data runs only once
Always check /var/log/cloud-init-output.log
Use set -ex
Add logging
Recreate instance if needed


sudo cat /var/log/user-data.log


sudo cat /var/log/cloud-init-output.log
